Top notes of Ugandan Vanilla, Dewdrop Floral Petals, Lotus and Bulgarian Rose. Heart notes of Jasmine, Freesia and Orchid. Base notes of White Amber, Sandalwood and Vanilla in Water. Experience the pure and simple pleasure of Pure DKNY Verbena Scent Spray, a sparkling scent that captures the brightness of fresh greenery. Striving to be socially and environmentally responsible, helping to make a difference, drop by drop. The fragrance is a delicate balance of raw materials and a refined structure: a wet, fresh fragrance that personifies the essence of DKNY. The central note of Verbena Basil has a citrusy, herbaceous quality that lends a distinctive crispness to the perfume. Fresh, natural and very pretty, Pure DKNY Verbena is a joyous scent. In order to help them to sustain their livelihood, the core note of Verbena Basil in Pure DKNY Verbena is sourced directly from farmers in Togo, Africa. DKNY works in partnership with those farmers and with CARE, a humanitarian organisation that aims to tackles global poverty and supports those in the world's poorest countries.
